import React from 'react';
import { FC } from "react";
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form'
import Col from "react-bootstrap/Col";
import Row from "react-bootstrap/Row";



export const PartnerScreen : FC = () => {

return(
    <Form>
  <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formPlaintextCity">
    <Form.Label column sm="2">
      Город
    </Form.Label>
    <Col sm="10">
      <Form.Control  readOnly defaultValue="Санкт-Петербург" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Group>
  <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formPlaintextStreet">
    <Form.Label column sm="2">
      Улица
    </Form.Label>
    <Col sm="10">
      <Form.Control  readOnly defaultValue="ул. Коломенская" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Group>
  <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formPlaintextHouseNumber">
    <Form.Label column sm="2">
      Номер дома
    </Form.Label>
    <Col sm="10">
      <Form.Control  readOnly defaultValue="48" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Group>
  <Form.Group as={Row} controlId="formPlaintextIdx">
    <Form.Label column sm="2">
      Индекс
    </Form.Label>
    <Col sm="10">
      <Form.Control  readOnly defaultValue="193100" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Group>
</Form>

)


    
}
